  "page": "Qano",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> <i>Khal</i></span><br />Qano</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\"><img alt=\"Dothraki.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/50px-Dothraki.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/75px-Dothraki.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/45/Dothraki.svg/100px-Dothraki.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">Khal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Qano</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khal\" title=\"Khal\">khal</a></i> who lived during the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>. He was one of the four <i>khals</i> that fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Field_of_Crows\" title=\"Field of Crows\">Field of Crows</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Khal Qano joined forces with Khals <a href=\"/index.php/Haro\" title=\"Haro\">Haro</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Loso\" title=\"Loso\">Loso</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Zhako\" title=\"Zhako\">Zhako</a> to fight against High King <a href=\"/index.php/Mazor_Alexi\" title=\"Mazor Alexi\">Mazor Alexi</a>, who had united all of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sarnori\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnori\">Sarnori</a> lesser kings to defend their homeland against the Dothraki hordes. The battle took place halfway between <a href=\"/index.php/Sarnath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sarnath\">Sarnath</a> and the ruins of <a href=\"/index.php/Kasath\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kasath\">Kasath</a>. The Sarnori <a href=\"/index.php/Chariot\" title=\"Chariot\">chariots</a> smashed the center of the Dothraki horde. Haro was trampled and died, while his riders fled, chased by Alexi and his cavalry. However, the escape was feigned and Haro's riders turned back, raining arrows on the Sarnori, while the other <i>khals</i> surrounded the Tall Men on all sides, with Qano's <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> attacking from the north.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qano&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_grasslands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Grasslands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404061927\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.065 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.247 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 491/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10406/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5429/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 658/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1082/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage